706838f-a.folder: Stagg Street & Union Avenue, Brooklyn, NY
706838f-a.text:
1.  Stagg Street, east of Union Ave., showing along the south side of Stagg Street, the demolition of homes which are to be replaced by modern
(F.H.A.) apartments.

September 27, 1935.
P. L. Sperr.

2.  S.E. corner of Stagg St. & Union Ave., B'klyn.

Sept. 24, 1941
P.L. Sperr, photographer
